<br>
My neutral just does not care what your goodie twoshoes or simplistic evil character does. Just day out of my way! (I mean that in the nicest possible way). <br>
<br>
A true neutral is a &quot;Live and Let Live&quot;. This can be very hard to pull off, but it is a lot of fun.<br>
